===Etymology===
{{blend|crap|fantastic}}

===Adjective===
{{en-adj-more}}

#(''coarse UK slang'') Intended to be perceived as fantastic, but actually perceived as extremely poor quality.
#:''That was the most '''craptastic''' movie I've ever seen!''

====Quotations====
